00:00:26.493 --> 00:00:30.330 position:7% line:83% align:start
Listen to me Fena!
This is important!

00:00:30.364 --> 00:00:32.934 position:16% line:83% align:start
Go to Eden --
[ Screams ]

00:00:32.967 --> 00:00:36.370 position:44% line:89% align:start
Fena!

00:00:36.403 --> 00:00:38.071 position:21% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru!

00:00:38.105 --> 00:00:41.876 position:5% line:83% align:start
No matter what, just stay alive,
and I'll find you!

00:00:41.910 --> 00:00:42.844 position:38% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru!

00:00:42.877 --> 00:00:44.411 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru!

00:00:44.444 --> 00:00:47.515 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru!!

00:00:47.549 --> 00:00:50.618 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:00:50.652 --> 00:00:53.287 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ Bell tolls ]

00:00:55.255 --> 00:01:00.227 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Fena vocalizes softly ]

00:01:00.260 --> 00:01:03.230 position:21% line:5% align:start
[ Tolling continues ]

00:01:03.263 --> 00:01:06.099 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Vocalizing continues ]

00:01:08.870 --> 00:01:11.238 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ Sea birds chirp ]

00:01:11.271 --> 00:01:13.373 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Vocalizing continues ]

00:01:13.407 --> 00:01:21.716 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:21.749 --> 00:01:23.083 position:27% line:89% align:start
Fena.

00:01:28.022 --> 00:01:33.528 position:19% line:5% align:start
[ Singing in Japanese ]

