♪♪

00:02:10.098 --> 00:02:19.406 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:19.439 --> 00:02:28.549 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:28.583 --> 00:02:37.659 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:37.692 --> 00:02:46.801 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:46.834 --> 00:02:56.209 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:57.745 --> 00:03:00.480 position:35% line:5% align:start
[ Laughter,
indistinct conversations ]

00:03:00.515 --> 00:03:04.952 position:13% line:5% align:start
[ Music plays in distance ]

00:03:09.289 --> 00:03:11.425 position:44% line:83% align:start
Soldier 1: Sure.
I've heard the rumors.

00:03:11.458 --> 00:03:13.326 position:13% line:83% align:start
Soldier 2: No.
She really is a beauty.

00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:14.929 position:7% line:89% align:start
An absolute vision!

00:03:14.962 --> 00:03:16.329 position:50% line:83% align:start
She can't be
that stunning.

00:03:16.363 --> 00:03:18.166 position:16% line:83% align:start
Then clearly
you haven't laid eyes on her.

00:03:18.198 --> 00:03:19.399 position:30% line:89% align:start
I only know the rumors.

00:03:19.433 --> 00:03:21.169 position:10% line:83% align:start
When you see her,
you'll get it.

00:03:21.201 --> 00:03:22.537 position:19% line:83% align:start
Her skin's
as pale as snow,

00:03:22.570 --> 00:03:24.672 position:10% line:83% align:start
and hair's silver
like moonlight.

00:03:24.706 --> 00:03:26.473 position:58% line:89% align:start
Really?

00:03:26.507 --> 00:03:29.510 position:19% line:83% align:start
Noble: So then, who won
the right of her first night?

00:03:29.544 --> 00:03:31.411 position:16% line:83% align:start
I hear it was
that young upstart.

00:03:31.445 --> 00:03:33.548 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ Scoffs ] You mean
that eccentric whelp?

00:03:33.581 --> 00:03:35.482 position:21% line:83% align:start
Now, now,
the real question is,

00:03:35.516 --> 00:03:38.485 position:5% line:83% align:start
does her skin stay white
when she's flushed?

00:03:38.519 --> 00:03:41.089 position:19% line:83% align:start
Noble: Well, you can wonder
all you want you old dog,

00:03:41.122 --> 00:03:42.657 position:33% line:89% align:start
you'll never find out.

00:03:42.690 --> 00:03:44.092 position:7% line:89% align:start
I beg your pardon?

00:03:44.125 --> 00:03:45.793 position:5% line:83% align:start
You speak as if you're not
in the same boat

00:03:45.827 --> 00:03:46.994 position:7% line:89% align:start
as the rest of us!

00:03:47.028 --> 00:03:48.796 position:58% line:83% align:start
Otto...
simmer down.

00:03:48.830 --> 00:03:50.932 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Laughter in distance ]

00:03:50.965 --> 00:03:53.266 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ German accent ]
We must hurry.

00:03:57.705 --> 00:03:59.707 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Panting ]

00:04:02.375 --> 00:04:05.079 position:21% line:83% align:start
Angie: You really do
have such lovely hair.

00:04:05.113 --> 00:04:06.781 position:21% line:83% align:start
The name really does
suite you, dear.

00:04:06.814 --> 00:04:09.382 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's clear why the call you
the White Marginal.

00:04:09.416 --> 00:04:11.986 position:33% line:83% align:start
Pretty soon,
men from all over the Continent

00:04:12.019 --> 00:04:13.888 position:19% line:89% align:start
will flock to see you.

00:04:13.921 --> 00:04:15.757 position:16% line:89% align:start
I don't care.

00:04:15.790 --> 00:04:18.358 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Scoffs ] Oh, geez.

00:04:18.391 --> 00:04:20.061 position:27% line:83% align:start
You're still holding out
for that guy?

00:04:20.094 --> 00:04:22.096 position:33% line:83% align:start
That black-eyed knight
of yours?

00:04:22.130 --> 00:04:24.098 position:41% line:83% align:start
You don't even know
if he's still alive.

00:04:24.132 --> 00:04:26.000 position:27% line:89% align:start
What was his name again?

00:04:26.033 --> 00:04:27.502 position:55% line:83% align:start
Yookie...
Yookoo?

00:04:27.535 --> 00:04:31.706 position:69% line:83% align:start
Mmph!
Hmm. Ooh, so scary.

00:04:31.739 --> 00:04:33.241 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Footsteps depart ]

00:04:33.273 --> 00:04:34.175 position:55% line:89% align:start
Angie...

00:04:34.208 --> 00:04:35.676 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:04:35.710 --> 00:04:36.978 position:44% line:89% align:start
I can't do this.

00:04:37.011 --> 00:04:39.247 position:47% line:83% align:start
I refuse to --
to just let some man

00:04:39.279 --> 00:04:41.281 position:47% line:83% align:start
I've never met
have his way with me.

00:04:41.314 --> 00:04:43.450 position:55% line:83% align:start
I won't!
They can't make me!

00:04:45.352 --> 00:04:46.554 position:52% line:89% align:start
Not again.

00:04:46.587 --> 00:04:48.122 position:30% line:83% align:start
We're still doing this,
seriously?

00:04:48.156 --> 00:04:50.258 position:16% line:83% align:start
Oh! Hang on!
I've gotta show you something.

00:04:50.290 --> 00:04:51.993 position:5% line:83% align:start
I have some brilliant plans
worked up

00:04:52.026 --> 00:04:53.493 position:5% line:89% align:start
for this exact occasion!

00:04:53.528 --> 00:04:55.229 position:13% line:83% align:start
Get over here,
and I'll walk you through them!

00:04:55.263 --> 00:04:56.831 position:61% line:83% align:start
[ Sighs ]
Come on!

00:04:56.864 --> 00:04:58.533 position:24% line:89% align:start
Behold.

00:04:58.566 --> 00:05:01.135 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh, wow.
You're all the way up to 23?

00:05:01.169 --> 00:05:02.537 position:58% line:89% align:start
Plan A!

00:05:02.570 --> 00:05:04.605 position:33% line:83% align:start
While everyone in town
is fast asleep --

00:05:04.639 --> 00:05:06.107 position:13% line:83% align:start
Let me stop you
right there.

00:05:06.140 --> 00:05:07.542 position:10% line:83% align:start
Does this island
ever sleep?

00:05:07.575 --> 00:05:10.978 position:41% line:83% align:start
Oh, uh, good point!
Next, plan B!

00:05:11.012 --> 00:05:12.547 position:52% line:83% align:start
While doing
my morning shopping,

00:05:12.580 --> 00:05:15.049 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll distract my escorts and
slip through the Torkia market

00:05:15.082 --> 00:05:16.851 position:55% line:83% align:start
and enter
the Ares District!

00:05:16.884 --> 00:05:19.620 position:5% line:83% align:start
[ Sighs ] I have seen
this plan already.

00:05:19.654 --> 00:05:22.557 position:52% line:83% align:start
Oh, right.
Moving along, then!

00:05:22.590 --> 00:05:23.991 position:58% line:89% align:start
Plan C!

00:05:24.025 --> 00:05:26.093 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna bribe the sentry
at the western gate, and then --

00:05:26.127 --> 00:05:28.095 position:5% line:83% align:start
Bribe him with what?
You've got no money.

00:05:28.129 --> 00:05:29.396 position:27% line:89% align:start
Then I-I'll use my body.

00:05:29.429 --> 00:05:31.766 position:5% line:83% align:start
Doesn't that defeat the purpose
of escaping?

00:05:31.799 --> 00:05:34.268 position:10% line:83% align:start
Excellent point!
I would never!

00:05:34.302 --> 00:05:37.638 position:7% line:83% align:start
Which means Plan C
won't work either!

00:05:37.672 --> 00:05:39.907 position:21% line:83% align:start
These aren't exactly
what I'd call "brilliant."

00:05:39.941 --> 00:05:40.975 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Yawns ]

00:05:41.008 --> 00:05:42.009 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Sighs ]

00:05:42.043 --> 00:05:44.344 position:33% line:89% align:start
No matter what I do...

00:05:44.377 --> 00:05:45.847 position:44% line:83% align:start
every single plan
I come up with

00:05:45.880 --> 00:05:47.915 position:47% line:83% align:start
basically boils
to needing money!

00:05:47.949 --> 00:05:49.183 position:5% line:89% align:start
I could've told you that.

00:05:49.217 --> 00:05:50.685 position:47% line:5% align:start
Without money,
I can't get on a ship,

00:05:50.718 --> 00:05:52.385 position:35% line:5% align:start
and even if I made it
to the Continent,

00:05:52.419 --> 00:05:54.255 position:52% line:5% align:start
I couldn't
support myself!

00:05:54.288 --> 00:05:56.123 position:7% line:5% align:start
Welcome to reality.

00:05:56.157 --> 00:05:57.558 position:19% line:5% align:start
Money makes
the world go round.

00:05:57.592 --> 00:05:59.359 position:47% line:83% align:start
And that's when
it hit me.

00:05:59.392 --> 00:06:01.428 position:13% line:83% align:start
I know how I can get my hands
on some money!

00:06:01.461 --> 00:06:03.164 position:5% line:89% align:start
Well, don't look at me.

00:06:03.197 --> 00:06:05.132 position:50% line:89% align:start
Not from you!

00:06:05.166 --> 00:06:07.235 position:58% line:83% align:start
Angie,
money is a funny thing.

00:06:07.268 --> 00:06:08.603 position:41% line:83% align:start
Where there's none,
there's none at all,

00:06:08.636 --> 00:06:11.038 position:35% line:83% align:start
but when money rains,
it pours!

00:06:11.072 --> 00:06:12.607 position:47% line:89% align:start
Which is why...

00:06:12.640 --> 00:06:15.943 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna steal that money
from someone who stole it first.

00:06:15.977 --> 00:06:18.713 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hang on, is that why
you put yourself up for auction?

00:06:18.746 --> 00:06:20.715 position:5% line:83% align:start
You were just trying
to find the rich guys?

00:06:20.748 --> 00:06:21.749 position:58% line:89% align:start
Plan D!

00:06:21.782 --> 00:06:23.851 position:52% line:83% align:start
Presenting
the Witch's Whammy.

00:06:23.885 --> 00:06:24.919 position:38% line:89% align:start
It's an aphrodisiac,

00:06:24.952 --> 00:06:26.787 position:50% line:83% align:start
but according
to Elza the apothecary,

00:06:26.821 --> 00:06:28.689 position:27% line:83% align:start
if you mix a double dose
into wine, bam!

00:06:28.723 --> 00:06:31.391 position:41% line:83% align:start
You've got yourself
an instant sleeping potion!

00:06:31.424 --> 00:06:32.860 position:44% line:89% align:start
At least I hope.

00:06:32.894 --> 00:06:34.729 position:5% line:83% align:start
[ Sighs ] You can't trust
that crazy lady.

00:06:34.762 --> 00:06:37.198 position:7% line:83% align:start
My plan is to use this to knock
out that pampered man child

00:06:37.231 --> 00:06:40.568 position:5% line:83% align:start
and help myself to all the money
he used to buy me with!

00:06:40.601 --> 00:06:42.503 position:13% line:83% align:start
You know guards
will be standing watch outside

00:06:42.536 --> 00:06:44.572 position:10% line:89% align:start
all night, right?

00:06:44.605 --> 00:06:47.675 position:19% line:83% align:start
The special suite is on the
Tower of Babylon's second floor.

00:06:47.708 --> 00:06:49.677 position:30% line:83% align:start
It overlooks the water,
so there won't be guards there.

00:06:49.710 --> 00:06:51.379 position:52% line:83% align:start
If I craft
a make-shift curtain rope,

00:06:51.411 --> 00:06:53.547 position:16% line:83% align:start
climbing down the tower wall
will be a breeze!

00:06:53.581 --> 00:06:55.249 position:7% line:89% align:start
You'll get caught.

00:06:55.283 --> 00:06:57.551 position:47% line:83% align:start
They won't even
be looking for me.

00:06:57.585 --> 00:06:59.253 position:52% line:83% align:start
They won't
because they'll think

00:06:59.287 --> 00:07:00.554 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm preoccupied in bed.

00:07:00.588 --> 00:07:01.923 position:52% line:83% align:start
By the time
anyone catches on,

00:07:01.956 --> 00:07:03.691 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'll be free and clear
on a ship headed

00:07:03.724 --> 00:07:05.960 position:41% line:83% align:start
for the Continent,
crossing the sea of hope

00:07:05.993 --> 00:07:09.931 position:27% line:83% align:start
with the wind at my back
and bathed in the morning light!

00:07:09.964 --> 00:07:12.700 position:5% line:83% align:start
Okay. What're the chances
the potion won't work?

00:07:12.733 --> 00:07:13.768 position:55% line:89% align:start
Not sure.

00:07:13.801 --> 00:07:15.970 position:10% line:83% align:start
Or that you won't
be able to get a boat.

00:07:16.003 --> 00:07:17.505 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm not sure, either.

00:07:17.538 --> 00:07:18.806 position:10% line:89% align:start
Your plan stinks.

00:07:18.839 --> 00:07:20.708 position:61% line:89% align:start
Argh!

00:07:20.741 --> 00:07:23.778 position:30% line:83% align:start
Well, adventures always
carry a bit of risk, Angie!

00:07:23.811 --> 00:07:26.347 position:5% line:83% align:start
Sorry, when did this
become an adventure?

00:07:26.380 --> 00:07:28.182 position:41% line:83% align:start
Say what you like,
but I'm setting out

00:07:28.215 --> 00:07:30.418 position:33% line:83% align:start
into a brave new world
tonight!

00:07:30.450 --> 00:07:32.586 position:50% line:83% align:start
And you can't
talk me out of it!

00:07:32.620 --> 00:07:34.522 position:16% line:83% align:start
Don't worry.
I won't stop you.

00:07:34.555 --> 00:07:36.624 position:10% line:83% align:start
Your dumb plan'll
do that for me.

00:07:36.657 --> 00:07:39.226 position:5% line:83% align:start
Anyway, they'll be coming
to get you soon.

00:07:39.260 --> 00:07:42.430 position:5% line:89% align:start
Let's get you ready.

00:07:42.462 --> 00:07:43.798 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Groans ]

00:07:43.831 --> 00:07:49.270 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:49.303 --> 00:07:54.976 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:55.009 --> 00:07:56.310 position:55% line:89% align:start
Angie...

00:07:56.344 --> 00:07:58.546 position:52% line:83% align:start
Do you know
what day this is?

00:07:58.579 --> 00:08:00.881 position:13% line:83% align:start
Doesn't matter.
The clock's ticking.

00:08:00.915 --> 00:08:03.651 position:38% line:83% align:start
Today marks 10 years
to the day.

00:08:03.684 --> 00:08:07.288 position:10% line:83% align:start
10 years since I washed ashore
on this island.

00:08:07.321 --> 00:08:12.660 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:08:12.693 --> 00:08:14.395 position:16% line:89% align:start
Manager: Fena, it's time.

00:08:14.428 --> 00:08:16.130 position:38% line:89% align:start
Let's go.

00:08:16.163 --> 00:08:21.502 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:08:21.535 --> 00:08:27.074 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:08:27.108 --> 00:08:29.643 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ Footsteps echo ]

00:08:29.677 --> 00:08:31.379 position:33% line:83% align:start
Listen, Fena.
Maxiver, Jr.

00:08:31.412 --> 00:08:32.380 position:27% line:89% align:start
is a bit of an--

00:08:32.413 --> 00:08:33.948 position:5% line:89% align:start
let's just say an odd fellow.

00:08:33.981 --> 00:08:35.116 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ Women giggle ]

00:08:35.149 --> 00:08:36.517 position:41% line:89% align:start
Pbhttt!

00:08:36.550 --> 00:08:38.853 position:16% line:83% align:start
His behavior
may be off-putting,

00:08:38.886 --> 00:08:40.654 position:5% line:83% align:start
but just give yourself
to him.

00:08:40.688 --> 00:08:41.856 position:13% line:83% align:start
You'll get used
to it.

00:08:41.889 --> 00:08:43.491 position:19% line:83% align:start
If he takes
a liking to you,

00:08:43.524 --> 00:08:45.192 position:10% line:83% align:start
he'll spend money
like water.

00:08:45.226 --> 00:08:47.995 position:5% line:83% align:start
Your cut will be 1/10
of whatever he spends here.

00:08:48.029 --> 00:08:50.664 position:16% line:83% align:start
And don't try
to fudge the numbers.

00:08:50.698 --> 00:08:53.634 position:27% line:83% align:start
Huh?
W-What's wrong?

00:08:53.667 --> 00:08:55.569 position:50% line:83% align:start
It's just...
the second floor.

00:08:55.603 --> 00:08:57.471 position:7% line:89% align:start
W-We went past it.

00:08:57.506 --> 00:08:58.706 position:50% line:89% align:start
Second floor?

00:08:58.739 --> 00:09:00.574 position:50% line:83% align:start
Oh, you mean
the traditional room.

00:09:00.608 --> 00:09:02.877 position:13% line:83% align:start
Yes, it was at
Junior's request.

00:09:02.910 --> 00:09:05.012 position:5% line:83% align:start
He's been granted the use
of the top floor

00:09:05.046 --> 00:09:08.282 position:5% line:89% align:start
for the entire evening.

00:09:08.315 --> 00:09:10.084 position:52% line:83% align:start
Did you say
top floor?

00:09:10.117 --> 00:09:12.420 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm free!</i>

00:09:12.453 --> 00:09:15.189 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Aah! Farewell, cruel world!</i>

00:09:15.222 --> 00:09:17.725 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Whimpers ]

00:09:17.758 --> 00:09:19.026 position:50% line:83% align:start
What's gotten
into you?

00:09:19.060 --> 00:09:20.961 position:38% line:89% align:start
Too high!

