00:17:40.260 --> 00:17:42.296 position:41% line:89% align:start
[ Panting heavily ]

00:17:42.329 --> 00:17:46.099 position:21% line:83% align:start
D-Did you say something...
Lady Fena?

00:17:46.133 --> 00:17:48.101 position:13% line:89% align:start
Should we rest?

00:17:48.135 --> 00:17:49.136 position:55% line:89% align:start
I'm fine.

00:17:49.169 --> 00:17:50.838 position:44% line:89% align:start
We need to hurry.

00:17:50.872 --> 00:17:52.272 position:10% line:83% align:start
You don't really
look so fine.

00:17:52.306 --> 00:17:53.708 position:24% line:83% align:start
No matter how slow
your pace,

00:17:53.741 --> 00:17:57.011 position:5% line:83% align:start
persevering and moving
ever onwards without rest...

00:17:57.045 --> 00:17:58.513 position:21% line:83% align:start
is always
the fastest...

00:17:58.546 --> 00:17:59.881 position:47% line:89% align:start
Not if you die!

00:17:59.914 --> 00:18:02.349 position:5% line:83% align:start
Are you sure you aren't the one
who wants to rest, Lady Fena?

00:18:02.382 --> 00:18:03.417 position:61% line:89% align:start
Argh.

00:18:03.450 --> 00:18:04.953 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Panting ]

00:18:04.986 --> 00:18:07.722 position:27% line:77% align:start
[ Bushes rustle ]
Hmm?

00:18:07.755 --> 00:18:09.824 position:24% line:89% align:start
Was that the wind?

00:18:09.857 --> 00:18:11.726 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ Shouts ]

00:18:11.759 --> 00:18:14.629 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:18:14.662 --> 00:18:16.196 position:47% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ] Otto!

00:18:16.229 --> 00:18:18.498 position:41% line:89% align:start
[ Muffled screams ]

00:18:18.533 --> 00:18:19.867 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:18:19.901 --> 00:18:21.736 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ Groans ]

00:18:21.769 --> 00:18:23.236 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hes not dead, yet.

00:18:23.270 --> 00:18:26.173 position:13% line:83% align:start
Cause I hit him
with the flat of my sword.

00:18:26.206 --> 00:18:27.508 position:10% line:77% align:start
[ Chuckles ]
Fena: [ Muffled ] Otto!

00:18:27.542 --> 00:18:28.710 position:58% line:89% align:start
Let go!

00:18:28.743 --> 00:18:32.145 position:50% line:89% align:start
Let go of me!

00:18:32.179 --> 00:18:34.983 position:5% line:83% align:start
Now that's quite enough,
little lady.

00:18:35.016 --> 00:18:36.985 position:50% line:83% align:start
[ Chuckles ]
Look at that.

00:18:37.018 --> 00:18:38.853 position:41% line:83% align:start
Her hair really is
as white as snow.

00:18:38.886 --> 00:18:40.454 position:55% line:83% align:start
Just like
the rumors say.

00:18:40.487 --> 00:18:42.289 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, they don't call her
the White Marginal

00:18:42.322 --> 00:18:43.891 position:24% line:89% align:start
for nothing, right?

00:18:43.925 --> 00:18:45.893 position:44% line:83% align:start
Soldier: Come on.
Let's kill her.

00:18:45.927 --> 00:18:49.063 position:21% line:83% align:start
Don't be
in such a rush!

00:18:49.097 --> 00:18:50.932 position:47% line:89% align:start
No one'll know.

00:18:50.965 --> 00:18:52.100 position:10% line:83% align:start
All we have to do
is throw her

00:18:52.132 --> 00:18:54.102 position:19% line:83% align:start
in the sea
when we're done.

00:18:54.134 --> 00:18:56.236 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yeah, the makos will
take it from there.

00:18:56.269 --> 00:18:58.472 position:30% line:83% align:start
Fena: <i>Save me.</i>
[ Sobbing ]

00:18:58.506 --> 00:19:00.742 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Please save me, Yukimaru!</i>

00:19:00.775 --> 00:19:03.711 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey don't leave me out.
I wanna piece of --

00:19:03.745 --> 00:19:05.680 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Whoosh ]

00:19:05.713 --> 00:19:06.648 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ Sword clangs ]
Huh?

00:19:06.681 --> 00:19:07.782 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's wrong?

00:19:07.815 --> 00:19:09.149 position:41% line:89% align:start
I dunno, he just --

00:19:09.182 --> 00:19:10.118 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Whoosh ]

00:19:10.150 --> 00:19:11.251 position:16% line:89% align:start
You drunk or something?!

00:19:11.284 --> 00:19:12.219 position:21% line:89% align:start
Get up and do your --

00:19:12.252 --> 00:19:13.688 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ Body thuds ]

00:19:13.721 --> 00:19:15.757 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ All gasp ]

00:19:15.790 --> 00:19:17.625 position:24% line:89% align:start
W-What's going on?

00:19:17.659 --> 00:19:18.993 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Whoosh ]

00:19:19.027 --> 00:19:20.094 position:30% line:77% align:start
[ Body thuds ]
[ Whoosh ]

00:19:20.128 --> 00:19:21.062 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gags ]

00:19:21.095 --> 00:19:22.295 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ Body thuds ]

00:19:22.329 --> 00:19:24.799 position:27% line:83% align:start
Now who's there?!
Come on, you coward!

00:19:24.832 --> 00:19:25.833 position:30% line:89% align:start
Show yourself!

00:19:28.036 --> 00:19:35.943 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:35.977 --> 00:19:38.146 position:10% line:89% align:start
Fena: <i>Everything fell silent.</i>

00:19:38.178 --> 00:19:42.817 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:42.850 --> 00:19:44.585 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>All I remember...</i>

00:19:44.619 --> 00:19:46.688 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>was the sound of metal cutting</i>

00:19:46.721 --> 00:19:48.221 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>through the night air,</i>

00:19:48.255 --> 00:19:51.693 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>a blade that gave off</i>
 <i>an eerie glow,</i>

00:19:51.726 --> 00:19:55.129 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>a helmet with antlers...</i>

00:19:55.163 --> 00:19:58.198 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>and those deep black eyes.</i>

00:19:58.231 --> 00:20:01.301 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:20:01.334 --> 00:20:03.805 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ Wind gusts ]

00:20:03.838 --> 00:20:13.681 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:20:13.715 --> 00:20:14.649 position:55% line:89% align:start
Oh, um...

00:20:14.682 --> 00:20:15.683 position:55% line:89% align:start
I, uh...

00:20:15.717 --> 00:20:16.984 position:38% line:89% align:start
Thank you for, uh...

00:20:17.018 --> 00:20:18.586 position:52% line:89% align:start
Hey, wait!

00:20:18.619 --> 00:20:19.787 position:61% line:89% align:start
I --

00:20:19.821 --> 00:20:21.189 position:47% line:89% align:start
I think, uh...

00:20:21.221 --> 00:20:23.691 position:52% line:83% align:start
I know you.
I know you, right?!

00:20:23.725 --> 00:20:25.593 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:20:25.626 --> 00:20:28.029 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Grunting ]

00:20:28.062 --> 00:20:30.598 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:20:30.631 --> 00:20:33.568 position:35% line:83% align:start
I remember your eyes.
We've met before.

00:20:33.601 --> 00:20:36.303 position:47% line:83% align:start
But I'm sorry,
if I'm mistaken.

00:20:36.336 --> 00:20:38.806 position:50% line:83% align:start
The thing is,
I haven't really met

00:20:38.840 --> 00:20:40.373 position:35% line:89% align:start
that many decent men.

00:20:40.407 --> 00:20:43.144 position:19% line:83% align:start
On this island, they're all
scoundrels and miscreants.

00:20:43.177 --> 00:20:45.312 position:44% line:83% align:start
They abuse women,
treating us like things,

00:20:45.345 --> 00:20:46.948 position:33% line:83% align:start
have terrible tempers,
and it's impossible

00:20:46.981 --> 00:20:48.149 position:50% line:83% align:start
to know what
they are thinking.

00:20:48.182 --> 00:20:49.483 position:61% line:83% align:start
Okay.
I'm rambling.

00:20:49.517 --> 00:20:50.752 position:41% line:83% align:start
But what I'm trying
to say is --

00:20:50.785 --> 00:20:53.121 position:47% line:83% align:start
is that you're
completely different!

00:20:53.154 --> 00:20:54.856 position:55% line:89% align:start
I mean...

00:20:54.889 --> 00:20:56.858 position:50% line:89% align:start
You're not...

00:20:56.891 --> 00:20:58.391 position:41% line:89% align:start
like them, is all.

00:20:58.425 --> 00:21:01.829 position:52% line:83% align:start
You're just
so different.

00:21:01.863 --> 00:21:03.030 position:58% line:89% align:start
You...

00:21:03.064 --> 00:21:04.832 position:50% line:89% align:start
You saved me.

00:21:04.866 --> 00:21:06.366 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:21:06.399 --> 00:21:08.435 position:41% line:89% align:start
You saved my life.

00:21:08.468 --> 00:21:11.806 position:38% line:89% align:start
Like you did before.

00:21:11.839 --> 00:21:13.975 position:50% line:89% align:start
I'm positive.

00:21:14.008 --> 00:21:15.977 position:44% line:89% align:start
I know I'm right.

00:21:16.010 --> 00:21:18.179 position:55% line:89% align:start
It's you.

00:21:18.212 --> 00:21:20.715 position:30% line:89% align:start
You came back, Yukima--

00:21:20.748 --> 00:21:24.752 position:47% line:89% align:start
Aah! [ Groans ]

00:21:28.689 --> 00:21:30.625 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ Body thuds ]

00:21:31.926 --> 00:21:35.096 position:19% line:83% align:start
Shitan: [ Sighing ] Well...
that didn't take long.

00:21:35.129 --> 00:21:36.664 position:7% line:89% align:start
Who even does that?

00:21:36.697 --> 00:21:39.466 position:21% line:83% align:start
Kaede: That was impactful,
to say the least.

00:21:39.499 --> 00:21:41.836 position:19% line:83% align:start
Enju: Yeah, but was it
a good idea, though?

00:21:41.869 --> 00:21:44.872 position:13% line:83% align:start
Sure, why not?
He's tying up loose ends.

00:21:44.906 --> 00:21:47.608 position:44% line:83% align:start
Shitan: At least
it doesn't put us in any danger.

00:21:56.383 --> 00:21:58.085 position:16% line:89% align:start
You're as chatty as ever.

00:21:58.119 --> 00:22:00.588 position:33% line:89% align:start
Mm, annoying.

00:22:05.126 --> 00:22:06.627 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:22:06.661 --> 00:22:09.230 position:30% line:83% align:start
Fena: <i>Out cold</i>
 <i>on the damp forest floor,</i>

00:22:09.263 --> 00:22:11.132 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>I lay dreaming...</i>

00:22:11.165 --> 00:22:14.168 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>of moments</i>
 <i>from a lifetime away.</i>

00:22:14.202 --> 00:22:17.271 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:22:17.305 --> 00:22:18.840 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Weakly ] Wait for me...

00:22:18.873 --> 00:22:21.676 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:22:21.709 --> 00:22:25.947 position:33% line:89% align:start
...Yukimaru.

